# ========================================
# ABYSS-MONOREPO — ROOT .gitignore
# Generated: 2026-04-15 · Audit: 2026-04-15-audit-clearance
# Owner: Dr. Ferdi Iskandar (Avvcenna+)
# ========================================
#
# GOLDEN RULE: core `.agent/` governance docs, `CLAUDE.md`, `pnpm-lock.yaml`,
#              shared `.cursor/` project config (rules, agents, hooks
#              entrypoints), `.cursorignore`, and `mcp.json.example` are
#              TRACKED BY DESIGN. Operational agent logs, reports, workflow
#              libraries, and local planning artifacts stay LOCAL ONLY. See the
#              load-bearing negations at the end. Local-only: `.mcp.json`
#              (secrets), `.claude/`, `.agent/sessions/`, `.agent/reports/`,
#              `.agent/workflows/`, and `docs/superpowers/`.
# ========================================

# ---- SECRETS & ENV (NEVER COMMIT) ----
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cert
